Reference

Metadata for all tables in this package

tables includes all table names, metadata lists the variables for each table and value_labels contains all labels for each variable.

tables

Student statistics tables ("21311 Statistik der Studenten")

metadata

Metadata containing the variables for each student statistics table

value_labels

Value labels for all variables in the student statistics tables

Data
